<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


知乎用户

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="7">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$an-sheng-92" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/an-sheng-92" class="zg-link" title="安生">安生</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$liu-yang-10-41" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/liu-yang-10-41" class="zg-link" title="刘炀">刘炀</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$cai-he-49-40" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/cai-he-49-40" class="zg-link" title="苦先生">苦先生</a></span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="968818" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">哇，还有男玻璃心啊。你纯粹是非常不自信，你应该以提高你个人价值水平为主要目标，而不是守住女朋友为目标，她看不上你，你怎么也留不住。


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
